data.name: DucatusCoin
data.description:
Ducatus claims to provide a combination of cryptocurrency infrastructure and a network marketing distribution system. It is claimed that it is leveraging the distribution power of a carefully structured network marketing system with the scalability, security, and durability of a robustly designed cryptocurrency which gives  Ducatus coins real and lasting value. It is further claimed that Ducatus members can buy and sell Ducatus mining credits and digital coins from the ducatus.network website.
